    "attributes": {
        "action": "Rename maternity leave to child bereavement leave for people who've lost babies.",
        "additional_details": "I think for those who have lost it would be helpful to get same time and pay but under a different name.\r\n",
        "background": "When my daughter died I was still entitled to maternity leave and pay, which was good. \r\n \r\nHowever it left me having to explain where the baby was when I said I was off on maternity. I felt like a fraud. ",
